ataraxia
>Ataraxia (rare: Ἀταραξία, English: Ataraxia) is a state of calm and steadfastness of mind. A state of mind that is undisturbed. A state of [calm] mind, free from violent passions and desires. It is a technical term in ancient Greek philosophy, the Hellenistic view of life, and the [Epicurean] philosophy of disposition.

[peace of mind].
[Peace]
